The_nine_rooms | mapped by .ignoranz @ deutschmaschine.de
_________________________________________________________


this map is the ultimative fun factor @ online play. you better use this map only for multiplayer with real players,
cause bots are too stupid. 
9 rooms ,in 8 of them are diffrent funny traps. where and what kind of traps... ? its your mission to find out ;)
the map got 24 spawnpoints and is a ak47 only map.

have fun!

install:
________

copy the bsp file into your steam/steamapps/YOURACCOUNT/counterstrike-source/cstrike/maps folder


___________________________

greetz
